9b7fad7d17ab25b39b84be1782160704","tid":243834,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青龍，又名蒼龍，在中國傳統文化中是四象之一，根據五行學說，它是代表東方的靈獸，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">為青色的龍</span>，五行屬木，代表的季節是春季，司風雷，滋生萬物。<br />\n<br />\nWikipedia <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n古代青色=藍色<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"9356395536c60924976eb1e57edaa1aba272d3c9","tid":243834,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"其實係黑色"},{"pid":"f3f4095ab15924d1d8e69713af949e39f0a435c7","tid":243834,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"青可以解黑色（明朝）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba29112fa4d353b9073a68285c1dae6b8761f2b3","tid":243834,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青天白日<br />\n<br />\n青出於藍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n青天白日: <br />\n請參考國民黨旗<br />\n<br />\n青出於藍，而勝於藍:<br />\n話說古代染布係由藍草整出黎嘅顏料染成，而個隻布嘅顏色，係blue<br />\n<br />\n所以，青色就係blue<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c23bf9c49647776f1f19f7dfa9c3a90c06cc5ec","tid":243834,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青可以解黑色（明朝）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource"},{"pid":"56dfa92dbb530c6c17a9f8cbe260c27922cc6ded","tid":243834,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"青眼白龍"},{"pid":"771b7b33788f6a52dab55c8a6a96fb42e54ca495","tid":243834,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"精出於男"},{"pid":"74de7c7dfad794d3452b1e99a85b03a63720c06e","tid":243834,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青天白日<br />\n<br />\n青出於藍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以吞食天地個關公先岩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sanguogame.com.cn/image/wof/guanyu3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanguogame.com.cn%2Fimage%2Fwof%2Fguanyu3.gif&h=da1da6a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f6b9293d20f1afbe34cdaa55b8bc3a20b023f6b","tid":243834,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"說文解字：「綠， 帛青黃色也。」<br />\n<br />\n青+黃=綠<br />\n<br />\n所以，青=blue <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n說文解字<br />\n<br />\n倉經切<br />\n<br />\n東方色也。木生火，从生、丹。丹青之信言象然。凡青之屬皆从青。"},{"pid":"a613e45277cdc9ec1c256525335d5ebc5b169bb7","tid":243834,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>說文解字：「綠， 帛青黃色也。」<br />\n<br />\n青+黃=綠<br />\n<br />\n所以，青=blue <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n說文解字<br />\n<br />\n倉經切<br />\n<br />\n東方色也。木生火，从生、丹。丹青之信言象然。凡青之屬皆从青。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97964ff1123dfff4ffc681073de4224bdf88fba4","tid":243834,"uid":35317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"古代嘅青有好多意思<br />\n青天=藍色<br />\n青草=綠色<br />\n青絲=黑色"},{"pid":"a8a6d6fd3b728e11fda5dfd924c063a74fe7f7a2","tid":243834,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古代嘅青有好多意思<br />\n青天=藍色<br />\n青草=綠色<br />\n青絲=黑色</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bb5a7418d5ba6f2b19432c6661e6a70310da29","tid":243834,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"Wiki:<br />\n青龍偃月刀是偃月刀的其中一種。根據文獻記載及出土文物中，偃月刀在<span style=\"color: red;\">宋朝</span>開始出現，因重量關係，主要用於練習臂力，非戰爭中的武器。<br />\n<br />\n青龍偃月刀既存在已經係一個大bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201f394e889ae866d018616e6cf425fc9ff82e42","tid":243834,"uid":93713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"ching 龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb38d5ad68883e5292de434b66ebaf8fd25b90ca","tid":243834,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"望下自己條J"}]}